default1.2 
defaultThe separation of Post Office Ltd (POL) and Royal Mail is the first known example in the world of a national mail operator being separated from its retail arm.
default&#xa0;
default1.3
default The NF
defaultSP warned the government that th
defaulte success of this
default separation 
defaultwas predicated upon substantial income from additional government work at post offices.
default 
